為執行中的應用程式重新排序

column1: Allows the app to move tasks to the foreground and background. The app may do this without your input.
column4: 允許應用程式將工作移至前景或背景。應用程式可以自行處理，您無須操作。

column1: Allows the app to enable the car mode.
column4: 允許應用程式啟用車用模式。

column1: Allows the app to end background processes of other apps. This may cause other apps to stop running.
column4: 允許應用程式終止其他應用程式的背景處理程序。這樣可能會導致其他應用程式停止運行。

column1: This app can appear on top of other apps
column4: 此應用程式可以出現在其他應用程式上

column1: This app can appear on top of other apps or other parts of the screen. This may interfere with normal app usage and change the way that other apps appear.
column4: 此應用程式可以出現在其他應用程式或螢幕的其他部分上。這可能會影響應用程式的正常使用，並變更其他應用程式的顯示方式。

column1: This app can run in the background. This may drain battery faster.
column4: 此應用程式可在背景中執行，這可能會加速耗電。

column1: This app can use data in the background. This may increase data usage.
column4: 此應用程式可在背景中使用數據，這可能會增加數據用量。

column1: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory. This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down the tablet.
column4: 允許應用程式設定本身的某些部分持續佔用記憶體。這樣可能會限制其他應用程式可用的記憶體，並拖慢平板電腦的運作速度。

column1: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory. This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down your Android TV device.
column4: 允許應用程式的部分功能持續佔用記憶體。這樣可能會限制其他應用程式的可用記憶體，並拖慢 Android TV 裝置的運行速度。

column1: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory. This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down the phone.
column4: 允許應用程式設定本身的某些部分持續佔用記憶體。這樣可能會限制其他應用程式可用的記憶體，並拖慢手機的運作速度。

column1: Allows the app to make use of foreground services.
column4: 允許應用程式使用前景服務。
測量應用程式儲存空間

column1: Allows the app to retrieve its code, data, and cache sizes
column4: 允許應用程式擷取本身的程式碼、資料和快取大小

column1: Allows the app to modify the system's settings data. Malicious apps may corrupt your system's configuration.
column4: 允許應用程式修改系統設定資料。惡意應用程式可能會毀壞系統設定。

column1: Allows the app to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the tablet and allow the app to slow down the overall tablet by always running.
column4: 允許應用程式在系統完成開機程序時立即自行啟動。這會加長平板電腦的開機時間，而且會因為系統一直執行該應用程式而拖慢平板電腦的整體運作速度。

column1: Allows the app to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start your Android TV device and allow the app to slow down the overall device by always running.
column4: 允許應用程式在系統完成開機程序後隨即自行啟動。這可能延長 Android TV 裝置的開機時間，並會因一直執行該應用程式而拖慢裝置的整體運行速度。

column1: Allows the app to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the app to slow down the overall phone by always running.
column4: 允許應用程式在系統完成開機程序時立即自行啟動。這會加長手機的開機時間，而且會因為系統一直執行該應用程式而拖慢手機的整體運作速度。

column1: Allows the app to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive use may make the tablet slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.
column4: 允許應用程式傳送在廣播結束後仍繼續存在的記憶廣播。過度使用可能會促使平板電腦過度使用記憶體，因而拖慢速度或造成不穩定。

column1: Allows the app to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive use may make your Android TV device slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.
column4: 允許應用程式傳送置頂廣播，並在廣播結束後仍然繼續。過度使用會佔用大量記憶體，可能會令 Android TV 減慢運行速度或無法穩定運行。

column1: Allows the app to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive use may make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.
column4: 允許應用程式傳送在廣播結束後仍繼續存在的記憶廣播。過度使用可能會促使手機過度使用記憶體，因而拖慢運行速度或造成不穩定。

column1: Allows the app to read data about your contacts stored on your tablet. Apps will also have access to the accounts on your tablet that have created contacts. This may include accounts created by apps you have installed. This permission allows apps to save your contact data, and malicious apps may share contact data without your knowledge.
column4: 允許應用程式讀取儲存在平板電腦上的聯絡人資料。應用程式亦可存取平板電腦上已建立聯絡人的帳戶，其中可能包括已安裝應用程式所建立的帳戶。這項權限允許應用程式儲存您的聯絡人資料，而惡意應用程式也可能在您不知情時擅自共用聯絡資料。

column1: Allows the app to read data about your contacts stored on your Android TV device. Apps will also have access to the accounts on your Android TV device that have created contacts. This may include accounts created by apps you have installed. This permission allows apps to save your contact data, and malicious apps may share contact data without your knowledge.
column4: 允許應用程式讀取儲存在 Android TV 裝置上的聯絡人資料。應用程式亦可存取 Android TV 裝置上已建立聯絡人的帳戶，其中可能包括已安裝應用程式所建立的帳戶。這項權限允許應用程式儲存您的聯絡人資料，而惡意應用程式也可能在您不知情時擅自共用聯絡資料。

column1: Allows the app to read data about your contacts stored on your phone. Apps will also have access to the accounts on your phone that have created contacts. This may include accounts created by apps you have installed. This permission allows apps to save your contact data, and malicious apps may share contact data without your knowledge.
column4: 允許應用程式讀取儲存在手機上的聯絡人資料。應用程式亦可存取手機上已建立聯絡人的帳戶，其中可能包括已安裝應用程式所建立的帳戶。這項權限允許應用程式儲存您的聯絡人資料，而惡意應用程式也可能在您不知情時擅自共用聯絡資料。

column1: Allows the app to modify the data about your contacts stored on your tablet. This permission allows apps to delete contact data.
column4: 允許應用程式修改儲存在平板電腦上的聯絡人資料。這項權限允許應用程式刪除聯絡人資料。

column1: Allows the app to modify the data about your contacts stored on your Android TV device. This permission allows apps to delete contact data.
column4: 允許應用程式修改儲存在 Android TV 裝置上的聯絡人資料。這項權限允許應用程式刪除聯絡人資料。

column1: Allows the app to modify the data about your contacts stored on your phone. This permission allows apps to delete contact data.
column4: 允許應用程式修改儲存在手機上的聯絡人資料。這項權限允許應用程式刪除聯絡人資料。

column1: This app can read your call history.
column4: 此應用程式可以讀取您的通話記錄。

column1: Allows the app to modify your tablet's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.
column4: 允許應用程式修改平板電腦的通話記錄，包括來電和已撥電話相關資料。惡意應用程式可能會藉此刪除或修改您的通話記錄。

column1: Allows the app to modify your Android TV device's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.
column4: 允許應用程式修改 Android TV 裝置的通話記錄，包括來電和撥出電話的相關資料。惡意應用程式可能會藉此清除或修改您的通話記錄。

column1: Allows the app to modify your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.
column4: 允許應用程式修改手機的通話記錄，包括來電和已撥電話相關資料。惡意應用程式可能會藉此刪除或修改您的通話記錄。

column1: Access body sensor data, like heart rate, while in use
column4: 在使用時存取人體感應器資料，例如心率

column1: Allows the app to access body sensor data, such as heart rate, temperature, and blood oxygen percentage, while the app is in use.
column4: 允許應用程式在使用時存取人體感應器資料，例如心率、體溫、血氧百分比等。

column1: Access body sensor data, like heart rate, while in the background
column4: 在背景執行時存取人體感應器資料，例如心率

column1: Allows the app to access body sensor data, such as heart rate, temperature, and blood oxygen percentage, while the app is in the background.
column4: 允許應用程式在背景執行時存取人體感應器資料，例如心率、體溫、血氧百分比等。

column1: This app can read all calendar events stored on your tablet and share or save your calendar data.
column4: 此應用程式可以讀取所有儲存在您的平板電腦的日曆活動，並分享或儲存您的日曆資料。

column1: This app can read all calendar events stored on your Android TV device and share or save your calendar data.
column4: 此應用程式可以讀取所有儲存在 Android TV 裝置上的日曆活動，並分享或儲存您的日曆資料。

column1: This app can read all calendar events stored on your phone and share or save your calendar data.
column4: 此應用程式可以讀取所有儲存在您的手機中的日曆活動，並分享或儲存您的日曆資料。

column1: add or modify calendar events and send email to guests without owners' knowledge
column4: 在機主不知情下，新增或修改日曆活動，以及發送電郵給嘉賓

column1: This app can add, remove, or change calendar events on your tablet. This app can send messages that may appear to come from calendar owners, or change events without notifying their owners.
column4: 此應用程式可以加入、移除或變更您的平板電腦中的日曆活動。此應用程式可以傳送看似來自日曆擁有者的訊息，或變更活動而不通知其擁有者。

column1: This app can add, remove, or change calendar events on your Android TV device. This app can send messages that may appear to come from calendar owners, or change events without notifying their owners.

column1: This app can add, remove, or change calendar events on your phone. This app can send messages that may appear to come from calendar owners, or change events without notifying their owners.
column4: 此應用程式可以加入、移除或變更您的手機中的日曆活動。此應用程式可以傳送看似來自日曆擁有者的訊息，或變更活動而不通知其擁有者。

column1: Allows the app to access extra location provider commands. This may allow the app to interfere with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.
column4: 允許應用程式存取額外的位置提供者指令。這項設定可能會使應用程式干擾 GPS 或其他位置來源的運作。

column1: access precise location only in the foreground
column4: 只在前景存取精確位置

column1: This app can get your precise location from location services while the app is in use. Location services for your device must be turned on for the app to get location. This may increase battery usage.
column4: 使用此應用程式時，應用程式可透過定位服務獲取您的精確位置。您的裝置必須開啟定位服務，才能讓應用程式獲取位置。這可能會增加電池用量。

column1: access approximate location only in the foreground
column4: 只在前景存取概略位置

column1: This app can get your approximate location from location services while the app is in use. Location services for your device must be turned on for the app to get location.
column4: 使用此應用程式時，應用程式可透過定位服務獲取您的概略位置。您的裝置必須開啟定位服務，才能讓應用程式獲取位置。

column1: This app can access location at any time, even while the app is not in use.
column4: 即使您不使用此應用程式，它仍可隨時存取位置。

column1: Allows the app to modify global audio settings such as volume and which speaker is used for output.
column4: 允許應用程式修改全域音頻設定，例如音量和用於輸出的喇叭。

column1: This app can record audio using the microphone while the app is in use.
column4: 此應用程式在使用期間可使用麥克風錄音。

column1: This app can record audio using the microphone at any time.
column4: 此應用程式可隨時使用麥克風錄音。
發送指令至 SIM 卡

column1: Allows the app to send commands to the SIM. This is very dangerous.
column4: 允許應用程式傳送指令到 SIM 卡。這項操作具有高危險性。

column1: This app can recognize your physical activity.
column4: 此應用程式可識別您的體能活動。

column1: This app can take pictures and record videos using the camera while the app is in use.
column4: 此應用程式在使用期間可使用相機拍照及錄影。

column1: take pictures and videos in the background
This app can take pictures and record videos using the camera at any time.
column4: 此應用程式可隨時使用相機拍照及錄影。

column1: Allow an application or service access to system cameras to take pictures and videos
column4: 允許應用程式或服務存取系統相機來拍照和攝錄

column1: This privileged or system app can take pictures and record videos using a system camera at any time. Requires the android.permission.CAMERA permission to be held by the app as well
column4: 這個獲特別權限的系統應用程式可以在任何時候使用系統相機來拍照和攝錄。此外，應用程式亦需要 android.permission.CAMERA 權限

column1: Allow an application or service to receive callbacks about camera devices being opened or closed.
column4: 允許應用程式或服務接收相機裝置開啟或關閉的相關回電。

column1: This app can receive callbacks when any camera device is being opened (by what application) or closed.
column4: 當任何相機裝置在開啟 (由應用程式) 或關閉時，此應用程式就能接收回電。

column1: Allows the app to control the vibrator.
column4: 允許應用程式控制震動。

column1: Allows the app to access the vibrator state.
column4: 允許應用程式存取震動狀態。

column1: Allows the app to call phone numbers without your intervention. This may result in unexpected charges or calls. Note that this doesn't allow the app to call emergency numbers. Malicious apps may cost you money by making calls without your confirmation.
column4: 允許應用程式繞過您自行撥打電話號碼，但可能會產生未預期的費用或撥打未預期的電話。注意：這項權限不允許應用程式撥打緊急電話。惡意應用程式可能未經您確認擅自撥打電話，增加您的支出。
使用 IMS 通話服務

column1: Allows the app to use the IMS service to make calls without your intervention.
column4: 允許應用程式自行使用 IMS 服務撥打電話。
讀取手機狀態和識別碼

column1: Allows the app to access the phone features of the device. This permission allows the app to determine the phone number and device IDs, whether a call is active, and the remote number connected by a call.
column4: 允許應用程式使用裝置的電話功能。這項權限允許應用程式確定手機號碼和裝置編號、是否正在通話中，以及所撥打的對方號碼。

column1: read basic telephony status and identity
column4: 讀取基本電話狀態和身分

column1: Allows the app to access the basic telephony features of the device.
column4: 允許應用程式存取裝置的基本電話功能。

column1: Allows the app to route its calls through the system in order to improve the calling experience.
column4: 允許應用程式透過系統轉接來電，以改善通話體驗。

column1: see and control calls through the system.
column4: 透過系統查看和控制通話。

column1: Allows the app to see and control ongoing calls on the device. This includes information such as call numbers for calls and the state of the calls.
column4: 允許應用程式查看和控制裝置上正在進行的通話，當中包括通話號碼和通話狀態等資訊。

column1: Exempt the app from restrictions to record audio.
column4: 移除應用程式的錄音限制。

column1: continue a call from another app
column4: 繼續進行來自其他應用程式的通話

column1: Allows the app to continue a call which was started in another app.
column4: 允許應用程式繼續進行在其他應用程式中開始的通話。

column1: Allows the app to access the phone numbers of the device.
column4: 允許應用程式存取裝置上的電話號碼。

column1: prevent your Android TV device from sleeping
column4: 防止 Android TV 裝置進入休眠狀態

column1: Allows the app to keep the car screen turned on.
column4: 允許應用程式保持汽車螢幕開啟。

column1: Allows the app to prevent the tablet from going to sleep.
column4: 允許應用程式防止平板電腦進入休眠狀態。

column1: Allows the app to prevent your Android TV device from going to sleep.
column4: 允許應用程式防止 Android TV 裝置進入休眠狀態。

column1: Allows the app to prevent the phone from going to sleep.
column4: 允許應用程式防止手機進入休眠狀態。

column1: Allows the app to use the tablet's infrared transmitter.
column4: 允許應用程式使用平板電腦的紅外線傳送器。

column1: Allows the app to use your Android TV device's infrared transmitter.
column4: 允許應用程式使用 Android TV 裝置的紅外線傳輸器。

column1: Allows the app to use the phone's infrared transmitter.
column4: 允許應用程式使用手機的紅外線傳送器。

column1: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper.
column4: 允許應用程式設定系統桌布。

column1: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper size hints.
column4: 允許應用程式設定有關系統桌布大小的提示。

column1: Allows the app to change the tablet's time zone.
column4: 允許應用程式更改平板電腦的時區。

column1: Allows the app to change your Android TV device's time zone.
column4: 允許應用程式變更 Android TV 裝置的時區。

column1: Allows the app to change the phone's time zone.
column4: 允許應用程式更改手機的時區。

column1: Allows the app to get the list of accounts known by the tablet. This may include any accounts created by applications you have installed.
column4: 允許應用程式取得平板電腦已知的帳戶清單，其中可能包括您安裝的應用程式所建立的任何帳戶。

column1: Allows the app to get the list of accounts known by your Android TV device. This may include any accounts created by applications you have installed.
column4: 允許應用程式取得 Android TV 裝置已知的帳戶清單，其中可能包括已安裝應用程式所建立的任何帳戶。

column1: Allows the app to get the list of accounts known by the phone. This may include any accounts created by applications you have installed.
column4: 允許應用程式取得手機已知的帳戶清單，其中可能包括您安裝的應用程式所建立的任何帳戶。

column1: Allows the app to view information about network connections such as which networks exist and are connected.
column4: 允許應用程式查看網絡連線相關資訊，例如有哪些網絡和已連接哪些網絡。

column1: Allows the app to create network sockets and use custom network protocols. The browser and other applications provide means to send data to the internet, so this permission is not required to send data to the internet.
column4: 允許應用程式建立網絡通訊端及使用自訂的網絡通訊協定。瀏覽器和其他應用程式提供傳送資料至互聯網的途徑，因此不需要這項權限來傳送資料至互聯網。

column1: Allows the app to change the state of network connectivity.
column4: 允許應用程式更改網絡連線狀態。

column1: Allows the app to change the state of tethered network connectivity.
column4: 允許應用程式更改已共用網絡的連線狀態。

column1: Allows the app to view information about Wi-Fi networking, such as whether Wi-Fi is enabled and name of connected Wi-Fi devices.

column1:
Device logs record what happens on your device. Apps can use these logs to find and fix issues.

Some logs may contain sensitive info, so only allow apps you trust to access all device logs. 

If you don’t allow this app to access all device logs, it can still access its own logs. Your device manufacturer may still be able to access some logs or info on your device. Learn more

column1:
You can share this device with other people by creating additional users. Each user has their own space, which they can customize with apps, wallpaper, and so on. Users can also adjust device settings like Wi‑Fi that affect everyone.

When you add a new user, that person needs to set up their space.

Any user can update apps for all other users. Accessibility settings and services may not transfer to the new user.
column4:
您可以建立其他使用者，與他人共用這部裝置。每位使用者都有屬於自己的空間，並可以自訂應用程式、桌布等等。此外，使用者也可以調整會影響所有人的裝置設定，例如 Wi‑Fi 設定。

新加入的使用者需要自行設定個人空間。

任何使用者都可以為所有其他使用者更新應用程式。無障礙功能設定和服務則未必適用於新的使用者。

column1:
With power notification controls, you can set an importance level from 0 to 5 for an app's notifications. 

Level 5 
- Show at the top of the notification list 
- Allow full screen interruption 
- Always peek 

Level 4 
- Prevent full screen interruption 
- Always peek 

Level 3 
- Prevent full screen interruption 
- Never peek 

Level 2 
- Prevent full screen interruption 
- Never peek 
- Never make sound and vibration 

Level 1 
- Prevent full screen interruption 
- Never peek 
- Never make sound or vibrate 
- Hide from lock screen and status bar 
- Show at the bottom of the notification list 

Level 0 
- Block all notifications from the app
column4:
通知控制項讓您設定應用程式通知的重要性 (0 至 5 級)。

""第 5 級"" 
- 在通知清單頂部顯示 
- 允許全螢幕騷擾 
- 一律顯示通知 

""第 4 級"" 
- 阻止全螢幕騷擾 
- 一律顯示通知 

""第 3 級"" 
- 阻止全螢幕騷擾 
- 永不顯示通知 

""第 2 級"" 
- 阻止全螢幕騷擾 
- 永不顯示通知 
- 永不發出聲響和震動 

""第 1 級"" 
- 阻止全螢幕騷擾 
- 永不顯示通知 
- 永不發出聲響和震動 
- 從上鎖畫面和狀態列中隱藏 
- 在通知清單底部顯示 

""第 0 級"" 
- 封鎖所有應用程式通知

column1: Chapter 11: The Wonderful Emerald City of Oz
column4: 第 11 章：奧茲國的奇妙翡翠城

column1:
Even with eyes protected by the green spectacles Dorothy and her friends were at first dazzled by the brilliancy of the wonderful City. The streets were lined with beautiful houses all built of green marble and studded everywhere with sparkling emeralds. They walked over a pavement of the same green marble, and where the blocks were joined together were rows of emeralds, set closely, and glittering in the brightness of the sun. The window panes were of green glass; even the sky above the City had a green tint, and the rays of the sun were green. 

There were many people, men, women and children, walking about, and these were all dressed in green clothes and had greenish skins. They looked at Dorothy and her strangely assorted company with wondering eyes, and the children all ran away and hid behind their mothers when they saw the Lion; but no one spoke to them. Many shops stood in the street, and Dorothy saw that everything in them was green. Green candy and green pop-corn were offered for sale, as well as green shoes, green hats and green clothes of all sorts. At one place a man was selling green lemonade, and when the children bought it Dorothy could see that they paid for it with green pennies. 

There seemed to be no horses nor animals of any kind; the men carried things around in little green carts, which they pushed before them. Everyone seeemed happy and contented and prosperous.
column4:
即使戴著綠色眼鏡保護雙眼，桃樂絲和她的朋友一開始還是被這座奇妙城市的耀眼光芒照得目眩神迷。街道兩旁都是以碧綠大理石砌成的美麗房屋，到處鑲滿閃閃發亮的翡翠。她們走過的路面同樣以碧綠大理石鋪砌而成，石板與石板之間鑲有一排排緊密相連的翡翠，在陽光的照耀下閃閃發亮。房屋的窗戶鑲嵌著翠綠玻璃，城市上空呈現淡綠色，就連陽光也散發著綠色光芒。

路上有很多行人，不論男女老幼都穿著綠色衣服，甚至皮膚也略帶綠色。他們好奇地盯著桃樂絲和她那群外貌奇特的夥伴，所有小孩一看到獅子都拔足而逃，各自躲到母親身後；然而，沒有人開口與他們交談。街道上的商店五花八門，桃樂絲發現店裡每件商品都是綠色的，有綠色的糖果和爆谷，還有綠色的鞋子、帽子和衣服。有位小販在路上售賣綠色檸檬水，當孩子們拿錢購買時，桃樂絲發現錢幣也是綠色的。

城裡似乎沒有馬，也沒有任何動物。居民都是推著綠色小車運載物品。每個人看起來都很開心滿足，一切都安定繁榮。

column1:
Use your face to unlock your phone or for authentication in apps, like when you sign in or approve a purchase.

Keep in mind:
You can only have one face set up at a time. To add another face, delete the current one.

Looking at the phone can unlock it when you don’t intend to.

Your phone can be unlocked by someone else if it’s held up to your face.

Your phone can be unlocked by someone who looks a lot like you, like an identical sibling.

column4: 指紋設定程序只需一至兩分鐘。如略過此步驟，您可於稍後在設定中加入指紋。

column1: When you see this icon, use your fingerprint for authentication, like when you sign in to apps or approve a purchase
column4: 看到此圖示時，請使用指紋驗證身分，以便執行特定操作，例如登入應用程式或核准購買交易

column1: Using your fingerprint to unlock your phone may be less secure than a strong pattern or PIN
column4: 相對於複雜的上鎖圖案或 PIN，指紋解鎖的安全性較低

column1: Fingerprint Unlock creates a unique model of your fingerprint to verify it\u2019s you. To create this fingerprint model during setup, you will take images of your fingerprint from different positions.
column4: 「指紋解鎖」功能會為您建立獨一無二的指紋模型，以便系統驗證您的身分。在設定期間，您必須拍攝指紋的各個部位，才能建立這個指紋模型。

column1: Fingerprint Unlock creates a unique model of your child\u2019s fingerprint to verify it\u2019s them. To create this fingerprint model during setup, they will take images of their fingerprint from different positions.
column4: 「指紋解鎖」功能會為您的子女建立獨一無二的指紋模型，以便系統驗證其身分。在設定期間，他們必須拍攝指紋的各個部位，才能建立這個指紋模型。

column1: When you use Pixel Imprint, images are used to update your fingerprint model. Images used to create your fingerprint model are never stored, but the fingerprint model is stored securely on your phone and never leaves the phone. All processing occurs securely on your phone.
column4: 使用 Pixel Imprint 時，系統會使用圖片來更新您的指紋模型。系統不會儲存您用來建立指紋模型的圖片，只會將指紋模型安全地存放在手機上，但絕不會傳送到手機以外的地方。整個處理過程都會安全地在手機上進行。

column1: When they use Pixel Imprint, images are used to update their fingerprint model. Images used to create your child\u2019s fingerprint model are never stored, but the fingerprint model is stored securely on the phone and never leaves the phone. All processing occurs securely on the phone.
column4: 使用 Pixel Imprint 時，系統會使用圖片來更新其指紋模型。系統不會儲存子女用來建立指紋模型的圖片，只會將指紋模型安全地存放在手機上，但絕不會傳送到手機以外的地方。整個處理過程都會安全地在手機上進行。

column1: You can delete your fingerprint images and model, or turn off Fingerprint Unlock at any time in Settings. Fingerprint images and models are stored on the phone until you delete them.
column4: 您隨時可以前往「設定」刪除指紋圖像和模型，或停用指紋解鎖功能。指紋圖像和模型會儲存在手機上，直到您刪除為止。

column1: You and your child can delete their fingerprint images and model, or turn off Fingerprint Unlock at any time in Settings. Fingerprint images and models are stored on the phone until they\u2019re deleted.
column4: 您和子女可隨時前往「設定」刪除指紋圖片和模型或停用「指紋解鎖」功能。指紋圖片和模型會儲存在手機上，直至其刪除為止。

column1: Your phone can be unlocked when you don\u2019t intend to, like if someone holds it up to your finger.
column4: 您的手機有可能會意外解鎖，例如有人讓您的手指觸碰到手機。

column1: Your child\u2019s phone can be unlocked when they don\u2019t intend to, like if someone holds it up to their finger.
column4: 您子女的手機有可能會意外解鎖，例如有人讓其手指觸碰到手機。

column1: For best results, use a screen protector that\u2019s Made for Google certified. With other screen protectors, your fingerprint may not work.

column1:
When an app is pinned, the pinned app may open other apps and personal data may be accessible. 

To use app pinning: 	
1. Turn on app pinning 	
2. Open Overview 	
3. Tap the app icon at the top of the screen, then tap Pin
column4:
固定應用程式後，該應用程式可開啟其他應用程式，亦能存取個人資料。

使用應用程式固定功能的步驟如下： 
1. 開啟應用程式固定功能 
2. 開啟 [概覽] 
3. 輕按畫面頂部的應用程式圖示，然後輕按 [固定]

column1:
When an app is pinned, the pinned app may open other apps and personal data may be accessible. 

If you want to securely share your device with someone, try using a guest user instead. 

To use app pinning: 	
1. Turn on app pinning 	
2. Open Overview 	
3. Tap the app icon at the top of the screen, then tap Pin
column4:
固定應用程式後，該應用程式可開啟其他應用程式，亦能存取個人資料。

如要安全地與他人共用裝置，建議您改用訪客使用者。

使用應用程式固定功能的步驟如下： 
1. 開啟應用程式固定功能 
2. 開啟「概覽」 
3. 輕按畫面頂部的應用程式圖示，然後輕按 [固定]

column1: Chapter 11: The Wonderful Emerald City of Oz
column4: 第 11 章：奧茲國的奇妙翡翠城

column1:
Even with eyes protected by the green spectacles Dorothy and her friends were at first dazzled by the brilliancy of the wonderful City. The streets were lined with beautiful houses all built of green marble and studded everywhere with sparkling emeralds. They walked over a pavement of the same green marble, and where the blocks were joined together were rows of emeralds, set closely, and glittering in the brightness of the sun. The window panes were of green glass; even the sky above the City had a green tint, and the rays of the sun were green. 

There were many people, men, women and children, walking about, and these were all dressed in green clothes and had greenish skins. They looked at Dorothy and her strangely assorted company with wondering eyes, and the children all ran away and hid behind their mothers when they saw the Lion; but no one spoke to them. Many shops stood in the street, and Dorothy saw that everything in them was green. Green candy and green pop-corn were offered for sale, as well as green shoes, green hats and green clothes of all sorts. At one place a man was selling green lemonade, and when the children bought it Dorothy could see that they paid for it with green pennies. 

There seemed to be no horses nor animals of any kind; the men carried things around in little green carts, which they pushed before them. Everyone seeemed happy and contented and prosperous.
column4:
即使戴著綠色眼鏡保護雙眼，桃樂絲和她的朋友一開始還是被這座奇妙城市的耀眼光芒照得目眩神迷。街道兩旁都是以碧綠大理石砌成的美麗房屋，到處鑲滿閃閃發亮的翡翠。她們走過的路面同樣以碧綠大理石鋪砌而成，石板與石板之間鑲有一排排緊密相連的翡翠，在陽光的照耀下閃閃發亮。房屋的窗戶鑲嵌著翠綠玻璃，城市上空呈現淡綠色，就連陽光也散發著綠色光芒。

路上有很多行人，不論男女老幼都穿著綠色衣服，甚至皮膚也略帶綠色。他們好奇地盯著桃樂絲和她那群外貌奇特的夥伴，所有小孩一看到獅子都拔足而逃，各自躲到母親身後；然而，沒有人開口與他們交談。街道上的商店五花八門，桃樂絲發現店裡每件商品都是綠色的，有綠色的糖果和爆谷，還有綠色的鞋子、帽子和衣服。有位小販在路上售賣綠色檸檬水，當孩子們拿錢購買時，桃樂絲發現錢幣也是綠色的。

城裡似乎沒有馬，也沒有任何動物。居民都是推著綠色小車運載物品。每個人看起來都很開心滿足，一切都安定繁榮。

column1:
The selected language on your mobile device has an available dictionary.
We recommend downloading the %1$s dictionary to improve your typing experience.

The download could take a minute or two over 3G. Charges may apply if you don't have an unlimited data plan.
If you are not sure which data plan you have, we recommend finding a Wi-Fi connection to start the download automatically.

Tip: You can download and remove dictionaries by going to Languages & input in the Settings menu of your mobile device.

您流動裝置上所選的語言有字典可供使用。
